<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8">
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, 		initial-scale=1,maximum-scale=1,user-scalable=no">
    	<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
		<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="black">
		<meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no" />
		<script src="../../script/flexible_css.js"></script>
		<script src="../../script/flexible.js"></script>
    	<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../../css/api.css"/>
    	<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../../css/commonWindow.css"/>
    	<title>注册登录</title>
    	<style>
    		header{
    			padding-top: 0.746666rem;
    			margin-left: 0.4rem;
    			margin-right: 0.4rem;
    		}
    		header .photo{
    			width: 0.96rem;
    			height: 0.96rem;	
    			vertical-align:middle;
    			border-radius: 0.373333rem;
    			overflow: hidden;
    		}
    		header .photo img{
    			width: 100%;
    			height: 100%;
    		}
    		header span{
    			margin-left: 0.266666rem;
    			font-size: 0.373333rem;
    			font-family:PingFang-SC-Medium;
    			color: #333;
    		}
    		header p{
    			color: #333;
    			font-size: 0.48rem;
    			font-family:PingFang-SC-Medium;
    			margin-top: 0.32rem;
    			margin-bottom: 1.066666rem;
    		}
    		.main .topBat{
    			font-size: 0.373333rem;
    			color: #999;
    			margin-bottom: 0.533333rem;
    			margin-left: 0.4rem;
    		}
    		.main li{
    			height: 2.133333rem;
    			box-sizing: border-box;
    			position: relative;
    			margin-left: 0.4rem;
    			margin-right: 0.4rem;
    		}
    		.main li:after{
    			content: '';
    			height: 1px;
    			background: #E1E1E1;
    			position: absolute;
    			top: 0;
    			left: 0;
    			right: 0;
    			transform: scaleY(.5);
    		}
    		.main li .photo{
    			width: 1.493333rem;
    			height: 1.493333rem;	
    			border-radius: 0.106666rem;
    			margin-right: 0.266666rem;
    		}
    		.main li .autor{
    			font-size: 0.48rem;
    			color: #333;
    			height: 0.666666rem;
    			line-height: 0.666666rem;
    		}
    		.main li .desc{
    			height: 0.586666rem;
    			line-height: 0.586666rem;
    			font-size: 0.426666rem;
    			color: #999;
    			margin-top: 0.213333rem;
    		}
    		.main li .right{
    			width: 0.533333rem;
    			height: 0.4rem;
    		}
    		.add{
    			height: 2.133333rem;
    			margin: 0 0.4rem;
    			padding-left: 0.453333rem;
    			padding-right: 0.293333rem;
    			position: relative;
    		}
    		.add:before{
    			content: '';
    			height: 1px;
    			background: #E1E1E1;
    			position: absolute;
    			top: 0;
    			left: 0;
    			right: 0;
    			transform: scaleY(.5);
    		}
    		.add:after{
    			content: '';
    			height: 1px;
    			background: #E1E1E1;
    			position: absolute;
    			bottom: 0;
    			left: 0;
    			right: 0;
    			transform: scaleY(.5);
    		}
    		.add .left img{
    			width: 0.586666rem;
    			height: 0.586666rem;
    			margin-right: 0.72rem;
    		}
    		.add span{
    			font-size: 0.48rem;
    			color: #333;
    		}
    		.add img.right{
    			width:0.186666rem;
    			height: 0.373333rem;
    		}
    		.footer{
    			display: flex;
    			justify-content: center;
    		}
    		.footer .reg{
    			width: 8.666666rem;
    			height: 1.173333rem;
    			background:#FF77A9;
    			border-radius: 0.586666rem;
    			margin-top:1.066666rem;
    			display: flex;
    			justify-content: center;
    		}
    		.footer .reg a{
    			font-size: 0.48rem;
    			color: #fff;
    			margin-top: 0.266666rem;
    		}
    	</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<header>
			<div class="username flex flex-align-center">
				<div class="photo">
					<img src="../../icon/icon.png" alt="" />
				</div>
				<span>丽柜 申请使用</span>
				</div>
				<p>你的微信头像、昵称、地区和性别信息</p>
		</header>
		<div class="main">
			<p class="topBat">你可以选择使用不同的个人信息登录</p>
			<ul>
				<li class="flex flex-align-center flex-pack-justify">
					<div class="left flex">
						<img class="photo" src="../../image/bg.png" alt="" />
						<div class="text">
							<p class="autor">大脸猫</p>
							<p class="desc">微信个人信息</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<img class="right" src="../../icon/checked.png" alt="" />
				</li>
			</ul>
			<div class="add flex flex-pack-justify flex-align-center">
				<div class="left flex">
					<img src="../../icon/add.png" alt="" />
					<span>新建头像昵称</span>
				</div>
				<img class="right" src="../../icon/right.png"/>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="footer">
			<div class="reg"><a href="#">同意</a></div>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>
